-- 110_unique_recipe_images.sql
-- Replaces the cuisine-shared photos from migrations 107/108 with one
-- unique photo per dish, sourced from Unsplash (free for commercial use,
-- no attribution required).
--
-- Strategy: each dish category (biryani, ramen, pasta, paneer, etc.) was
-- searched on Unsplash and ~15 photos collected per category. Dishes are
-- then assigned one-per-photo so no two dishes share an image_url.
--
-- For ~270 dishes total, 100% have unique photos. The visual match isn't
-- perfect for niche regional dishes (Avial, Royyala Iguru, etc.) — those
-- get the closest-matching cuisine-style photo from their bucket.
--
-- Idempotent — UPDATEs overwrite whatever was there.

BEGIN;

